channel.title: [Delta] Interface Images [Delta]
channel.description: I made an interface for my server using Lin's Interface Maker and I used some of my own images. I put the images in my cache/sprites folder and the methods in my class9 class. I compiled and ran my client, when I logged in and looked to the interface I added, it doesn't have any of the images, it just shows the text. How can I make the images show?
